comments: DeRozan (CHI) gathers the ball on his left foot and does not take more than two steps after his gather.
Bitadze (ORL) brushes DeRozan's (CHI) arm and marginal contact occurs as he gathers and enters his upward shooting motion.  Bitadze then cleanly blocks DeRozan's shot.
Bitadze (ORL) cleanly blocks DeRozan's (CHI) shot attempt before the ball reaches its apex.
Vucevic (CHI) swipes his hand down and initiates contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) is already in Wagner's (ORL) path and is firming up over his left foot when contact occurs.
Vucevic (CHI) brings his arm towards Bitadze's (ORL) front, and the contact off ball during Dosunmu's (CHI) shot attempt is marginal.
Vucevic (CHI) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
DeRozan (CHI) brings his lower body towards Isaac (ORL), and marginal contact occurs as the rebound bounces away from their matchup.
Vucevic (CHI) is already in Isaac's (ORL) path and is firming up over his right leg when contact occurs.
Bitadze (ORL) swipes his hand down and initiates contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm, and the contact occurs after DeRozan's gather.
Dosunmu (CHI) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
White (CHI) establishes himself in Isaac's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Wagner (ORL) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) cleanly deflects the loose ball away from Caruso (CHI).
DeRozan (CHI) faces up with Isaac (ORL) and impedes his pursuit of the rebound.
After the ball becomes loose, Dosunmu (CHI) and Wagner (ORL) both meet at the same point and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Banchero (ORL) does not step out of bounds when he receives the pass.
Banchero's (ORL) shot does not make contact with the rim within 24 seconds.
Isaac (ORL) is moving alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.

White (CHI) avoids making contact with Wagner (ORL) during his drive to the basket.  However, Dosunmu (CHI) steps forward into Wagner's path and initiates foot to foot contact with Wagner that affects his SQBR.  The foul should have been assessed to Dosunmu.
Dosunmu (CHI) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) delivers contact with his side as he sets the pick on Isaac (ORL).
Vucevic (CHI) grabs and pulls Wagner's (ORL) jersey away from his body, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Isaac (ORL) and Caruso (CHI) pursue the rebound, and incidental contact occurs as Caruso deflects the ball.
DeRozan (CHI) initiates contact with Bitadze's (ORL) arm and affects his ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Banchero (ORL) is jumping to DeRozan's (CHI) side, and marginal contact occurs with DeRozan's slightly extended knee during the dunk attempt.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Wagner (ORL).
